{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015UHQzRirKrwxJTp9g2HKLM","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the code, here's a summary of the available closecall infrastructure for building transactions:\n\n## PDA Helper Functions\nLocated in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`:\n\n1. **`getCloseCallRoundPda(roundId: Uint8Array)`**\n   - Derives the round PDA using seeds: `[\"cc_round\", round_id (8 bytes)]`\n   - Returns: `[PublicKey, number]` (PDA address and bump)\n\n2. **`getCloseCallConfigPda()`**\n   - Derives the global config PDA using seed: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n   - Returns: `[PublicKey, number]` (PDA address and bump)\n\n## Program ID\n- **`CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID`**: Derived from `ClosecallIDL.address`\n- **Value**: `8TXq2XyHsk5AAMkoyk5QtG25xyyY7rTMHXrJRHRwjUpA`\n\n## IDL Structure (High-Level Overview)\nThe IDL at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json` defines:\n\n### Instructions (5 total):\n1. **`create_round`** — Create a new round with open price from Pyth\n   - Accounts: server, config (PDA), round (PDA), price_update, system_program\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n2. **`place_bet`** — Place a bet on a side (Green=0 or Red=1)\n   - Accounts: player, config (PDA), round (PDA), system_program\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8]), side (u8), amount (u64)\n\n3. **`settle_round`** — Settle the round with close price and distribute payouts\n   - Accounts: caller, round (PDA), config (PDA), price_update, treasury, rent_receiver\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n4. **`force_close`** — Admin-only force close with refunds\n   - Accounts: authority, round (PDA), config (PDA), rent_receiver\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n5. **`timeout_refund`** — Permissionless refund after deadline\n   - Accounts: caller, round (PDA), config (PDA), rent_receiver\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n6. **`initialize_config`** — Initialize global config (admin)\n   - Accounts: authority, config (PDA), system_program\n   - Args: treasury (pubkey), pyth_feed_id (u8[32]), betting_window_secs (u32), max_entries_per_side (u8)\n\n### Account Types:\n- **`CloseCallRound`** — Stores entries, pools, prices, phase, outcome\n- **`CloseCallConfig`** — Stores authority, treasury, Pyth feed ID, betting window, max entries, paused flag\n\n### Enums:\n- **`CloseCallPhase`**: Open, Settled, Refunded\n- **`Outcome`**: Pending, Green, Red, Refund\n\n### Data Structures:\n- **`BetEntry`**: player (pubkey), amount_lamports (u64)\n\nAll exported from `@rng-utopia/game-engine`:\n```typescript\nexport {\n  CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID,\n  getCloseCallRoundPda,\n  getCloseCallConfigPda,\n} from \"./closecall\";\n```"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a804fe71bc14e991f (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 43435\ntool_uses: 4\nduration_ms: 12461</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3173b348-180a-4cf2-ac38-47c17bdb617e","uuid":"7cd9fbfd-a07b-41bb-8292-649fdae71040","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the following files to understand what's already available for building closecall transactions:\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/index.ts`\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts`\n4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json` (the IDL)\n\nReport the PDA helper functions, program IDs, and IDL structure available for closecall.","agentId":"a804fe71bc14e991f","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the code, here's a summary of the available closecall infrastructure for building transactions:\n\n## PDA Helper Functions\nLocated in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`:\n\n1. **`getCloseCallRoundPda(roundId: Uint8Array)`**\n   - Derives the round PDA using seeds: `[\"cc_round\", round_id (8 bytes)]`\n   - Returns: `[PublicKey, number]` (PDA address and bump)\n\n2. **`getCloseCallConfigPda()`**\n   - Derives the global config PDA using seed: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n   - Returns: `[PublicKey, number]` (PDA address and bump)\n\n## Program ID\n- **`CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID`**: Derived from `ClosecallIDL.address`\n- **Value**: `8TXq2XyHsk5AAMkoyk5QtG25xyyY7rTMHXrJRHRwjUpA`\n\n## IDL Structure (High-Level Overview)\nThe IDL at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json` defines:\n\n### Instructions (5 total):\n1. **`create_round`** — Create a new round with open price from Pyth\n   - Accounts: server, config (PDA), round (PDA), price_update, system_program\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n2. **`place_bet`** — Place a bet on a side (Green=0 or Red=1)\n   - Accounts: player, config (PDA), round (PDA), system_program\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8]), side (u8), amount (u64)\n\n3. **`settle_round`** — Settle the round with close price and distribute payouts\n   - Accounts: caller, round (PDA), config (PDA), price_update, treasury, rent_receiver\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n4. **`force_close`** — Admin-only force close with refunds\n   - Accounts: authority, round (PDA), config (PDA), rent_receiver\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n5. **`timeout_refund`** — Permissionless refund after deadline\n   - Accounts: caller, round (PDA), config (PDA), rent_receiver\n   - Args: round_id (u8[8])\n\n6. **`initialize_config`** — Initialize global config (admin)\n   - Accounts: authority, config (PDA), system_program\n   - Args: treasury (pubkey), pyth_feed_id (u8[32]), betting_window_secs (u32), max_entries_per_side (u8)\n\n### Account Types:\n- **`CloseCallRound`** — Stores entries, pools, prices, phase, outcome\n- **`CloseCallConfig`** — Stores authority, treasury, Pyth feed ID, betting window, max entries, paused flag\n\n### Enums:\n- **`CloseCallPhase`**: Open, Settled, Refunded\n- **`Outcome`**: Pending, Green, Red, Refund\n\n### Data Structures:\n- **`BetEntry`**: player (pubkey), amount_lamports (u64)\n\nAll exported from `@rng-utopia/game-engine`:\n```typescript\nexport {\n  CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID,\n  getCloseCallRoundPda,\n  getCloseCallConfigPda,\n} from \"./closecall\";\n```"}],"totalDurationMs":12461,"totalTokens":43435,"totalToolUseCount":4,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13179,"cache_read_input_tokens":29341,"output_tokens":908,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":13179},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
