{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YDRWH2KbC8qVxxFeq6cQ73","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. Now I have a complete understanding of the CloseCall program. Let me compile and present the comprehensive report.\n\n## CloseCall Program Analysis: Accounts, PDAs, and Instructions\n\n### State Structures\n\n**CloseCallConfig**\n- **PDA seeds**: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n- **Fields**:\n  - `authority` (Pubkey) — admin authority\n  - `treasury` (Pubkey) — fee destination wallet\n  - `pyth_feed_id` ([u8; 32]) — Pyth price feed ID for BTC/USD\n  - `betting_window_secs` (u32) — betting window duration (default 30s)\n  - `max_entries_per_side` (u8) — maximum entries per side (default 32)\n  - `paused` (bool) — whether game is paused\n  - `bump` (u8) — PDA bump seed\n\n**CloseCallRound**\n- **PDA seeds**: `[\"cc_round\", &round_id]` where `round_id` is [u8; 8] backend-generated\n- **Fields**:\n  - `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — backend-generated round identifier\n  - `server` (Pubkey) — server wallet that paid rent and will settle\n  - `phase` (CloseCallPhase) — Open | Settled | Refunded\n  - `green_entries` (Vec<BetEntry>) — green (bull) bets [max_len(32)]\n  - `red_entries` (Vec<BetEntry>) — red (bear) bets [max_len(32)]\n  - `green_pool` (u64) — total lamports in green side\n  - `red_pool` (u64) — total lamports in red side\n  - `open_price` (i64) — Pyth open price (scaled integer)\n  - `open_price_expo` (i32) — Pyth price exponent at round creation\n  - `close_price` (i64) — Pyth close price at settlement (0 until settled)\n  - `created_at` (i64) — Unix timestamp when round was created\n  - `betting_ends_at` (i64) — Unix timestamp when betting window closes\n  - `resolve_deadline` (i64) — Unix timestamp after which timeout_refund is available\n  - `outcome` (Outcome) — Pending | Green | Red | Refund\n  - `total_fee` (u64) — fee collected (0 for refund rounds)\n  - `bump` (u8) — PDA bump seed\n\n**BetEntry**\n- `player` (Pubkey) — player address\n- `amount_lamports` (u64) — bet amount\n\n### Instructions\n\n---\n\n#### **1. initialize_config**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `treasury` (Pubkey) — treasury wallet address\n- `pyth_feed_id` ([u8; 32]) — Pyth BTC/USD feed ID\n- `betting_window_secs` (u32) — betting window duration\n- `max_entries_per_side` (u8) — max entries per side\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `authority` | Yes | Yes | — | Authority signer, pays for account rent |\n| `config` | Yes | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Initialized PDA |\n| `system_program` | — | — | — | System program |\n\n---\n\n#### **2. create_round**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — backend-generated round ID\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `server` | Yes | Yes | — | Server wallet; pays rent for round account |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config PDA (validation only) |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `init, payer=server, seeds=[b\"cc_round\", round_id.as_ref()], bump` | Initialized round PDA |\n| `price_update` | — | — | — | **CHECK: Pyth PriceUpdateV2**; parsed & validated for feed_id and freshness (MAX_OPEN_PRICE_AGE_SECS = 60s) |\n| `system_program` | — | — | — | System program |\n\n**Round State Initialization**:\n- `phase` ← `Open`\n- `green_entries` ← empty\n- `red_entries` ← empty\n- `green_pool` ← 0\n- `red_pool` ← 0\n- `open_price` ← Pyth current price\n- `open_price_expo` ← Pyth exponent\n- `close_price` ← 0\n- `created_at` ← current timestamp\n- `betting_ends_at` ← now + betting_window_secs\n- `resolve_deadline` ← now + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS (60s) + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS (300s) = now + 360s\n- `outcome` ← `Pending`\n- `total_fee` ← 0\n\n---\n\n#### **3. place_bet**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — round identifier\n- `side` (u8) — 0 = Green (bull), 1 = Red (bear)\n- `amount` (u64) — bet amount in lamports\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `player` | Yes | Yes | — | Player wallet; signer and wager source |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config validation (pause check) |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `seeds=[b\"cc_round\", round_id.as_ref()], bump=round.bump` | Round PDA (stores bet) |\n| `system_program` | — | — | — | System program |\n\n**Validations**:\n- Round phase must be `Open`\n- Current time < `betting_ends_at`\n- Wager amount ≥ minimum (0.0026 SOL)\n- Player has not already bet in this round (checked across both sides)\n- Target side has < max_entries_per_side entries\n\n**Effects**:\n- Transfer amount from player to round PDA\n- Append BetEntry to green_entries or red_entries\n- Increment green_pool or red_pool\n\n---\n\n#### **4. settle_round**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — round identifier\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `caller` | Yes | Yes | — | Backend settlement signer |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `mut, close=rent_receiver, seeds=[b\"cc_round\", &round_id], bump=round.bump` | Round PDA (closed after settlement) |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config validation |\n| `price_update` | — | — | — | **CHECK: Pyth PriceUpdateV2**; parsed & validated for feed_id and freshness (MAX_CLOSE_PRICE_AGE_SECS = 120s) |\n| `treasury` | Yes | — | — | **CHECK: Must match config.treasury** |\n| `rent_receiver` | Yes | — | — | **CHECK: Must match round.server** (receives rent on close) |\n| `remaining_accounts` (dynamic) | Yes | — | — | Decided outcome: winning bettors (1 per winner in entry order) OR Refund outcome: all bettors [green_0..green_n, red_0..red_m] |\n\n**Validations**:\n- Round phase must be `Open`\n- Current time ≥ candle_close_time (created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS)\n- Close price exponent matches open price exponent\n- treasury == config.treasury\n- rent_receiver == round.server\n- remaining_accounts.len() matches expected count (1 for decisive outcomes, total_count for refunds)\n\n**Outcome Determination**:\n- **Refund** if: no bets, only one side has bets, single total bet, or close_price == open_price\n- **Green** if: both sides present, multiple bets, and close_price > open_price\n- **Red** if: both sides present, multiple bets, and close_price < open_price\n\n**Payout Logic (Decisive)**:\n- Calculate total pool fee using `calculate_net_payout` (3% fee)\n- Distribute net pool to winning bettors proportionally to their stake\n- Last winner gets remainder to avoid dust\n- Transfer fee to treasury\n\n**Payout Logic (Refund)**:\n- Return full bet amount to each player\n\n**State Updates**:\n- `phase` ← `Settled` (decisive) or `Refunded` (refund)\n- `close_price` ← close price from Pyth\n- `outcome` ← determined outcome\n- `total_fee` ← collected fee (0 for refund)\n- Round PDA closed; rent transferred to rent_receiver (server)\n\n**Event Emitted**: `RoundSettled` with round_id, outcome, open_price, close_price, green_pool, red_pool, total_fee, num_winners\n\n---\n\n#### **5. timeout_refund**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — round identifier\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `caller` | Yes | Yes | — | Any signer (permissionless after deadline) |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `mut, close=rent_receiver, seeds=[b\"cc_round\", &round_id], bump=round.bump` | Round PDA (closed after refunds) |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config validation (validation only) |\n| `rent_receiver` | Yes | — | — | **CHECK: Must match round.server** (receives rent on close) |\n| `remaining_accounts` (dynamic) | Yes | — | — | All player wallets [green_0..green_n, red_0..red_m] in entry order |\n\n**Validations**:\n- Round phase must be `Open`\n- Current time ≥ resolve_deadline (created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS)\n- rent_receiver == round.server\n- remaining_accounts.len() == total_count (green_count + red_count)\n\n**Effects**:\n- Refund each player their full bet amount from round PDA\n- Set phase ← `Refunded`\n- Set outcome ← `Refund`\n- Round PDA closed; rent transferred to rent_receiver (server)\n\n---\n\n### Timeline Constants\n\n- **CANDLE_DURATION_SECS**: 60 (time from creation to price close)\n- **RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS**: 300 (grace period after candle close for settlement)\n- **Total window**: ~360 seconds before permissionless timeout_refund available"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a24cb912b6842b560 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 44143\ntool_uses: 7\nduration_ms: 27301</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3173b348-180a-4cf2-ac38-47c17bdb617e","uuid":"a25db1a1-b3b4-4ffa-9c7f-c9ebea8a152a","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the closecall program instruction files to understand the accounts required for each instruction. Read:\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/create_round.rs`\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/settle_round.rs`\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/timeout_refund.rs`\n4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/mod.rs`\n5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs`\n\nReport all account structs (with their constraints), PDA seeds, and instruction arguments for create_round, settle_round, and timeout_refund.","agentId":"a24cb912b6842b560","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. Now I have a complete understanding of the CloseCall program. Let me compile and present the comprehensive report.\n\n## CloseCall Program Analysis: Accounts, PDAs, and Instructions\n\n### State Structures\n\n**CloseCallConfig**\n- **PDA seeds**: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n- **Fields**:\n  - `authority` (Pubkey) — admin authority\n  - `treasury` (Pubkey) — fee destination wallet\n  - `pyth_feed_id` ([u8; 32]) — Pyth price feed ID for BTC/USD\n  - `betting_window_secs` (u32) — betting window duration (default 30s)\n  - `max_entries_per_side` (u8) — maximum entries per side (default 32)\n  - `paused` (bool) — whether game is paused\n  - `bump` (u8) — PDA bump seed\n\n**CloseCallRound**\n- **PDA seeds**: `[\"cc_round\", &round_id]` where `round_id` is [u8; 8] backend-generated\n- **Fields**:\n  - `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — backend-generated round identifier\n  - `server` (Pubkey) — server wallet that paid rent and will settle\n  - `phase` (CloseCallPhase) — Open | Settled | Refunded\n  - `green_entries` (Vec<BetEntry>) — green (bull) bets [max_len(32)]\n  - `red_entries` (Vec<BetEntry>) — red (bear) bets [max_len(32)]\n  - `green_pool` (u64) — total lamports in green side\n  - `red_pool` (u64) — total lamports in red side\n  - `open_price` (i64) — Pyth open price (scaled integer)\n  - `open_price_expo` (i32) — Pyth price exponent at round creation\n  - `close_price` (i64) — Pyth close price at settlement (0 until settled)\n  - `created_at` (i64) — Unix timestamp when round was created\n  - `betting_ends_at` (i64) — Unix timestamp when betting window closes\n  - `resolve_deadline` (i64) — Unix timestamp after which timeout_refund is available\n  - `outcome` (Outcome) — Pending | Green | Red | Refund\n  - `total_fee` (u64) — fee collected (0 for refund rounds)\n  - `bump` (u8) — PDA bump seed\n\n**BetEntry**\n- `player` (Pubkey) — player address\n- `amount_lamports` (u64) — bet amount\n\n### Instructions\n\n---\n\n#### **1. initialize_config**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `treasury` (Pubkey) — treasury wallet address\n- `pyth_feed_id` ([u8; 32]) — Pyth BTC/USD feed ID\n- `betting_window_secs` (u32) — betting window duration\n- `max_entries_per_side` (u8) — max entries per side\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `authority` | Yes | Yes | — | Authority signer, pays for account rent |\n| `config` | Yes | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Initialized PDA |\n| `system_program` | — | — | — | System program |\n\n---\n\n#### **2. create_round**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — backend-generated round ID\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `server` | Yes | Yes | — | Server wallet; pays rent for round account |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config PDA (validation only) |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `init, payer=server, seeds=[b\"cc_round\", round_id.as_ref()], bump` | Initialized round PDA |\n| `price_update` | — | — | — | **CHECK: Pyth PriceUpdateV2**; parsed & validated for feed_id and freshness (MAX_OPEN_PRICE_AGE_SECS = 60s) |\n| `system_program` | — | — | — | System program |\n\n**Round State Initialization**:\n- `phase` ← `Open`\n- `green_entries` ← empty\n- `red_entries` ← empty\n- `green_pool` ← 0\n- `red_pool` ← 0\n- `open_price` ← Pyth current price\n- `open_price_expo` ← Pyth exponent\n- `close_price` ← 0\n- `created_at` ← current timestamp\n- `betting_ends_at` ← now + betting_window_secs\n- `resolve_deadline` ← now + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS (60s) + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS (300s) = now + 360s\n- `outcome` ← `Pending`\n- `total_fee` ← 0\n\n---\n\n#### **3. place_bet**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — round identifier\n- `side` (u8) — 0 = Green (bull), 1 = Red (bear)\n- `amount` (u64) — bet amount in lamports\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `player` | Yes | Yes | — | Player wallet; signer and wager source |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config validation (pause check) |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `seeds=[b\"cc_round\", round_id.as_ref()], bump=round.bump` | Round PDA (stores bet) |\n| `system_program` | — | — | — | System program |\n\n**Validations**:\n- Round phase must be `Open`\n- Current time < `betting_ends_at`\n- Wager amount ≥ minimum (0.0026 SOL)\n- Player has not already bet in this round (checked across both sides)\n- Target side has < max_entries_per_side entries\n\n**Effects**:\n- Transfer amount from player to round PDA\n- Append BetEntry to green_entries or red_entries\n- Increment green_pool or red_pool\n\n---\n\n#### **4. settle_round**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — round identifier\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `caller` | Yes | Yes | — | Backend settlement signer |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `mut, close=rent_receiver, seeds=[b\"cc_round\", &round_id], bump=round.bump` | Round PDA (closed after settlement) |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config validation |\n| `price_update` | — | — | — | **CHECK: Pyth PriceUpdateV2**; parsed & validated for feed_id and freshness (MAX_CLOSE_PRICE_AGE_SECS = 120s) |\n| `treasury` | Yes | — | — | **CHECK: Must match config.treasury** |\n| `rent_receiver` | Yes | — | — | **CHECK: Must match round.server** (receives rent on close) |\n| `remaining_accounts` (dynamic) | Yes | — | — | Decided outcome: winning bettors (1 per winner in entry order) OR Refund outcome: all bettors [green_0..green_n, red_0..red_m] |\n\n**Validations**:\n- Round phase must be `Open`\n- Current time ≥ candle_close_time (created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS)\n- Close price exponent matches open price exponent\n- treasury == config.treasury\n- rent_receiver == round.server\n- remaining_accounts.len() matches expected count (1 for decisive outcomes, total_count for refunds)\n\n**Outcome Determination**:\n- **Refund** if: no bets, only one side has bets, single total bet, or close_price == open_price\n- **Green** if: both sides present, multiple bets, and close_price > open_price\n- **Red** if: both sides present, multiple bets, and close_price < open_price\n\n**Payout Logic (Decisive)**:\n- Calculate total pool fee using `calculate_net_payout` (3% fee)\n- Distribute net pool to winning bettors proportionally to their stake\n- Last winner gets remainder to avoid dust\n- Transfer fee to treasury\n\n**Payout Logic (Refund)**:\n- Return full bet amount to each player\n\n**State Updates**:\n- `phase` ← `Settled` (decisive) or `Refunded` (refund)\n- `close_price` ← close price from Pyth\n- `outcome` ← determined outcome\n- `total_fee` ← collected fee (0 for refund)\n- Round PDA closed; rent transferred to rent_receiver (server)\n\n**Event Emitted**: `RoundSettled` with round_id, outcome, open_price, close_price, green_pool, red_pool, total_fee, num_winners\n\n---\n\n#### **5. timeout_refund**\n\n**Arguments**:\n- `round_id` ([u8; 8]) — round identifier\n\n**Accounts**:\n\n| Account | Mutable | Signer | PDA Constraint | Notes |\n|---------|---------|--------|---|----------|\n| `caller` | Yes | Yes | — | Any signer (permissionless after deadline) |\n| `round` | Yes | — | `mut, close=rent_receiver, seeds=[b\"cc_round\", &round_id], bump=round.bump` | Round PDA (closed after refunds) |\n| `config` | — | — | `seeds=[b\"closecall_config\"], bump=config.bump` | Config validation (validation only) |\n| `rent_receiver` | Yes | — | — | **CHECK: Must match round.server** (receives rent on close) |\n| `remaining_accounts` (dynamic) | Yes | — | — | All player wallets [green_0..green_n, red_0..red_m] in entry order |\n\n**Validations**:\n- Round phase must be `Open`\n- Current time ≥ resolve_deadline (created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS)\n- rent_receiver == round.server\n- remaining_accounts.len() == total_count (green_count + red_count)\n\n**Effects**:\n- Refund each player their full bet amount from round PDA\n- Set phase ← `Refunded`\n- Set outcome ← `Refund`\n- Round PDA closed; rent transferred to rent_receiver (server)\n\n---\n\n### Timeline Constants\n\n- **CANDLE_DURATION_SECS**: 60 (time from creation to price close)\n- **RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS**: 300 (grace period after candle close for settlement)\n- **Total window**: ~360 seconds before permissionless timeout_refund available"}],"totalDurationMs":27301,"totalTokens":44143,"totalToolUseCount":7,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2160,"cache_read_input_tokens":39121,"output_tokens":2855,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2160},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
